@startuml
title Аутентификация пользователя - Диаграмма последовательности

actor "Владелец дома" as User
participant "Веб-приложение" as WebApp
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "Auth Controller" as AuthCtrl
participant "Authentication Service" as AuthSvc
participant "2FA Service" as TwoFA
participant "Password Hasher" as Hasher
participant "Token Manager" as TokenMgr
participant "User Repository" as UserRepo
participant "SMS Adapter" as SMSAdapter
participant "SMS-шлюз" as SMSGW
participant "БД PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Event Publisher" as EventPub
participant "Message Queue" as Kafka

== Шаг 1: Первичная аутентификация ==

User -> WebApp: Вводит телефон и пароль
WebApp -> APIGateway: POST /api/auth/login\n{phone: "+79161234567", password: "***"}
APIGateway -> AuthCtrl: Маршрутизация запроса

activate AuthCtrl
AuthCtrl -> AuthSvc: authenticate(phone, password)

activate AuthSvc
AuthSvc -> UserRepo: find_by_phone(phone)

activate UserRepo
UserRepo -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE phone = ?
activate DB
DB --> UserRepo: UserData(hashed_password, 2fa_enabled=true)
deactivate DB
UserRepo --> AuthSvc: User(hashed_password, 2fa_enabled)
deactivate UserRepo

AuthSvc -> Hasher: check_password(password, hashed_password)
activate Hasher
Hasher --> AuthSvc: true (пароль верный)
deactivate Hasher

alt 2FA включена
    AuthSvc -> TwoFA: generate_code(user_id)
    activate TwoFA
    TwoFA -> TwoFA: create_2fa_code(6 digits)
    TwoFA --> AuthSvc: code: "123456"
    deactivate TwoFA

    AuthSvc -> SMSAdapter: send_sms(phone, "Ваш код: 123456")
    activate SMSAdapter
    SMSAdapter -> SMSGW: HTTP POST /send-sms
    activate SMSGW
    SMSGW --> SMSAdapter: 200 OK (SMS отправлено)
    deactivate SMSGW
    SMSAdapter --> AuthSvc: sent
    deactivate SMSAdapter

    AuthSvc --> AuthCtrl: 2FA_REQUIRED
    deactivate AuthSvc

    AuthCtrl --> APIGateway: 202 Accepted\n{status: "2fa_required", message: "Требуется подтверждение"}
    APIGateway --> WebApp: Response
    WebApp --> User: Запрос 2FA кода

else 2FA выключена
    AuthSvc -> TokenMgr: generate_token(user_id, role)
    activate TokenMgr
    TokenMgr --> AuthSvc: JWT: "eyJhbGci..."
    deactivate TokenMgr

    AuthSvc --> AuthCtrl: AuthSuccess(token, user_data)
    deactivate AuthSvc

    AuthCtrl --> APIGateway: 200 OK\n{token: "JWT...", user: {...}}
    APIGateway --> WebApp: Response
    WebApp --> User: Вход выполнен (перенаправление в кабинет)
end

APIGateway --> WebApp: Response
WebApp --> User: Отображает результат (успех/ошибка)

@enduml